<H3> <TI>   Deputies View New Defense Minister Choice </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deputies View New Defense Minister Choice </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1429A Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA in Russian 27 Apr 94 p 
1 </F>

<F P=103> 944K1429A </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
